snippet.title: Rising Hell Trailer - Arok Reborn
snippet.description:
Rising Hell is a vertical platformer rogue-lite filled with adrenaline-pumping action and tons of heavy gothic metal shreds. Climb out from the ever-changing hell while you fight hordes of blood-lusting demons!

Out now on Steam Early Access
🔥 http://bit.ly/risinghellsteam

Follow Rising Hell for more updates
🔥 https://twitter.com/risinghellgame
🔥 https://facebook.com/RisingHellGame/

-----

Developer: Tahoe Games
Publisher: Toge Productions
